-eat the rice slowly, or not at all
-cook the meats without sauce first. Then after you cook the marinated meats, ask for a new grill
-you can cut the large pieces of meat over the grill so the cuttings land on the grill to cook
-pull the hose down if the grill starts to smoke
-pull cooked meats to the edge of the grill to keep them warm while you eat and toss the next meat on the grill
-order more meat before you've cooked everything at the table
